Accommodation Options ](https://tokyocheapo.com/accommodationcat/accommodation-guide-2014/)\n    * [ Flights to Tokyo ](https://tokyocheapo.com/travel/cheap-flights-to-tokyo-guide/)\n    * [ Rail Passes ](https://tokyocheapo.com/travel/transport/which-jr-rail-pass-to-choose/)\n    * [ Shinkansen Tickets ](https://affiliate.klook.com/redirect?aid=513&aff_adid=746479&k_site=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.klook.com%2Frails-32%2F1012-japan%2F%3Fspm%3DMobility_Aggregate.SubTransportation_LIST)\n    * [ Renting Pocket Wifi ](https://tokyocheapo.com/business/internet/rent-wifi-router-japan/)\n    * [ Japan SIM Cards ](https://tokyocheapo.com/business/internet/prepaid-cheap-japan-sim-card-options/)\n    * [ Tokyo Guide Book ](https://tokyocheapo.com/book/?utm_source=top_menu&utm_medium=tokyocheapo.com&utm_campaign=internal_book_links)\n    * [ Tokyo Transport System ](https://tokyocheapo.com/travel/)\n    * [ Top Tokyo attractions ](https://tokyocheapo.com/attractions/)\n    * [ Travel Insurance ](https://tokyocheapo.com/editorial/travel-health-insurance-japan/)\n  * [ Jobs ](https://creative.tokyocheapo.com/ \"Jobs\")\n  * [ Tours ](https://tokyocheapo.com/tours/ \"Tours\")\n\n\n  * [ Events ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events \"Events\")\n  * [ Eating ](https://tokyocheapo.com/food-and-drink \"Eating\")\n  * [ Tours ](https://tokyocheapo.com/tours \"Tours\")\n  * [ Stay ](https://tokyocheapo.com/accommodation/all \"Stay\")\n  * [ Jobs ](https://creative.tokyocheapo.com \"Jobs\")\n\n\n![Family](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2013/05/childrens-tree-house-Chris-Kirkland-1024x600.jpg)\nPic: Chris Kirkland\n# Family\n  * [Home](https://tokyocheapo.com)\n  * [Things to do in Tokyo](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/)\n\n\nDespite having a population in decline, Tokyo is an amazing place for family activities, with countless adventures both indoors and out, as well as generous ticket reductions for kids. \n## Playgrounds and Parks\nPlaygrounds are a serious business here, check out these [free ones](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/family/free-playgrounds-in-tokyo/) and for a day out consider [Niko Niko park](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/family/nico-nico-park-cheap-fun-with-the-kids) which is fenced in and even has a summer beer-garden you can make the most your kids running wild. There’s a free [Moomin-themed park](https://tokyocheapo.com/lifestyle/outdoors/where-dreams-come-true-the-free-moomin-themed-park-in-saitama/) in Saitama which is as magical as you would hope. \n## Child-friendly Museums and Galleries\nFor interactive museums and art galleries [this guide](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/family/9-free-fun-places-take-kids-tokyo) will get you started; from earthquake-simulators to [cup ramen making](https://tokyocheapo.com/food-and-drink/ramen/yokohama-cup-noodles-museum/) to gas science museums, there’s something for even the most curious of minds. Just scraping past the definition of museum, the [Studio Ghibli Museum](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/art/lose-your-way-at-the-ghibli-museum/) is a magical place if they enjoy the films (and even if they don’t) while [Teamlab Planets](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/art/everything-you-need-to-know-about-teamlab-planets/) offers a truly immersive experience. \n## Theme Parks: Old and New\nHowever, if it’s thrills, nostalgia and bizarrely flavored popcorn they’ve got their tiny hearts set on, fear not, Tokyo Disneyland and the equally fun Tokyo DisneySea don’t have to break the bank—here’s our [guide](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/5-tips-for-saving-money-at-tokyo-disneyland-and-tokyo-disneysea/) to saving where you can. Although, the more traditional Japanese theme parks can offer a great day out, without the queues and high prices, [Hanayashiki](https://tokyocheapo.com/lifestyle/hanayashiki-japans-oldest-amusement-park-in-tokyo/) in Asakusa is a great alternative. For more [bonus themepark options](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/themeparks-and-zoos/tokyo-disneyland-alternatives/) read on, with Sanrio PuroLand being a cute favorite among [Hello Kitty fans](https://tokyocheapo.com/shopping-2/tokyo-for-hello-kitty-fans/). \n## Themed Cafes\nWhen you’re tired out from family activities galore, themed cafes are a great way to take a break and keep the kids entertained, with numerous characters served up in foam and sugar forms, from Alice in Wonderland in Shibuya to Pom Pom Purin in Harajuku. We have a full list of our [favorite themed options](https://tokyocheapo.com/food-and-drink/tokyo-themed-restaurants/) to choose from (but not all are child-friendly).\nIf they miss the pets or just really love rabbits, an animal cafe could be a great plan—with our guide to the [ethical alternatives here](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/animal-cafes-in-tokyo-alternatives/), (although keep in mind that some have age restrictions). Whatever it is you need—you’ll have plenty of choice in Tokyo!\n_If you’re looking for souvenirs for the little ones left at home – we’ve got the[best toy stores in Tokyo for you](https://tokyocheapo.com/shopping-2/tokyo-toy-stores/) too._\nFeatured Posts\n  * [ ![](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/04/tokyodisneyland1-notext-1024x576.jpg) Featured New Video! Tokyo Disneyland: Everything to Know Before Visiting  ](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/family/new-video-tokyo-disneyland-everything-to-know-before-visiting/ \"New Video! Tokyo Disneyland: Everything to Know Before Visiting\")\nApril 26, 2024 | Aimee Gardner \nEasy to reach and a guaranteed great day out if you’re a Disney fan. \n[Family](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/family/) [Themeparks and Zoos](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/themeparks-and-zoos/)\n  * [ ![Rollercoaster and ferris wheel at Tokyo Dome](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2016/07/tokyo-dome-attractions_gdl-1024x768.jpg) Featured 6 Fun and Frightening Alternatives to Tokyo Disneyland and DisneySea  ](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/themeparks-and-zoos/tokyo-disneyland-alternatives/ \"6 Fun and Frightening Alternatives to Tokyo Disneyland and DisneySea\")\nMay 25, 2022 | Lily Crossley-Baxter \nIf Disney isn’t your dream but you love a good theme park then Tokyo will not disappoint - choose from hello kitty rides to record-breaking roller-coasters.\n[Family](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/family/) [Themeparks and Zoos](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/themeparks-and-zoos/)\n  * [ ![Robot+Robot interior - tokyo toy stores](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/01/robot-robot-interior_gdl-1024x768.jpg) Featured Best Toy Stores in Tokyo  ](https://tokyocheapo.com/shopping-2/tokyo-toy-stores/ \"Best Toy Stores in Tokyo\")\nJuly 26, 2021 | Lucy Dayman \nA selection of some not-to-be-missed Tokyo toy stores and mega centers selling mainstream and niche items.\n[Family](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/family/) [Shopping](https://tokyocheapo.com/shopping-2/)\n  * [ ![](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2013/05/Moomin-house-1000yen-entrance-Chris-Kirkland-1-1024x768.jpg) Featured Complete Guide to Visiting the New Moomin Theme Park  ](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/family/moomin-theme-park-saitama/ \"Complete Guide to Visiting the New Moomin Theme Park\")\nApril 2, 2019 | Felix Wilson \nEverything you need to know about visiting the new Moomin theme park in Saitama. Plus an impressive and free Moomin park alternative! \n[Family](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/family/)\n\n\nLatest Posts\n  * [ ![Tokyo Disneyland](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/07/Walt-Disney-statue-castle-Victor-Gonzalez-1024x683.jpg) ](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/themeparks-and-zoos/5-tips-for-saving-money-at-tokyo-disneyland-and-tokyo-disneysea/ \"How to Save Money at Tokyo Disneyland — Tickets & Tips\")\n###  [ How to Save Money at Tokyo Disneyland — Tickets & Tips ](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/themeparks-and-zoos/5-tips-for-saving-money-at-tokyo-disneyland-and-tokyo-disneysea/ \"How to Save Money at Tokyo Disneyland — Tickets & Tips\")\nSeptember 18, 2023 | Mareike Dornhege \nA bit of magic, for a bit less cash.\n[Family](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/family/) [Themeparks and Zoos](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/themeparks-and-zoos/)\n  * [ ![japan rabbit island](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2019/05/Japan-rabbit-island-iStock-mitumal-1024x683.jpg) ](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/animal-cafes-in-tokyo-alternatives/ \"Cool, Not Cruel: Alternatives to Mainstream Animal Cafes\")\n###  [ Cool, Not Cruel: Alternatives to Mainstream Animal Cafes ](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/animal-cafes-in-tokyo-alternatives/ \"Cool, Not Cruel: Alternatives to Mainstream Animal Cafes\")\nMay 1, 2019 | Carey Finn \nWhere to get your dose of cute 'n' fluffy, minus the cruelty. Includes lots of cat photos.\n[Family](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/family/) [Things to do in Tokyo](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/)\n  * [ ![](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2018/10/iStock-disneyland-mumemories-1024x683.jpg) ](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/themeparks-and-zoos/tokyo-disneysea-guide/ \"The Know-Before-You-Go Guide to Tokyo DisneySea\")\n###  [ The Know-Before-You-Go Guide to Tokyo DisneySea ](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/themeparks-and-zoos/tokyo-disneysea-guide/ \"The Know-Before-You-Go Guide to Tokyo DisneySea\")\nMarch 13, 2019 | Tiffany \nRead our tips for an even more magical day.\n[Family](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/family/) [Themeparks and Zoos](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/themeparks-and-zoos/)\n  * [ ![places to take kids tokyo](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2014/12/Design-Festa.jpg) ](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/family/9-free-fun-places-take-kids-tokyo/ \"9 Free and Fun Places to Take Your Kids in Tokyo\")\n###  [ 9 Free and Fun Places to Take Your Kids in Tokyo ](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/family/9-free-fun-places-take-kids-tokyo/ \"9 Free and Fun Places to Take Your Kids in Tokyo\")\nApril 9, 2016 | Jason Andrew Jenkins \nTokyo abounds with family-friendly interactive museums and art galleries to keep the little ones entertained. \n[Family](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/family/)\n  * [ ![](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/01/7670327636_55a59e56b0_o-1024x683.jpg) ](https://tokyocheapo.com/lifestyle/hanayashiki-amusement-park-in-tokyo/ \"Hanayashiki: Japan’s Oldest Amusement Park\")\n###  [ Hanayashiki: Japan’s Oldest Amusement Park ](https://tokyocheapo.com/lifestyle/hanayashiki-amusement-park-in-tokyo/ \"Hanayashiki: Japan’s Oldest Amusement Park\")\nFebruary 7, 2015 | Tiffany \nQuick! Name an amusement park in Japan. Tokyo Disney Resort and Universal Studios Japan (USJ) will probably come to mind. But what about we focus on a homegrown Japanese theme park for a change? It’s time to get acquainted with [[…]](https://tokyocheapo.com/lifestyle/hanayashiki-amusement-park-in-tokyo/)\n[Family](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/family/) [Lifestyle](https://tokyocheapo.com/lifestyle/) [Things to do in Tokyo](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/)\n  * [ ![](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2013/08/bridge.jpg) ](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/family/free-playgrounds-in-tokyo/ \"The Best Free Playgrounds in Tokyo\")\n###  [ The Best Free Playgrounds in Tokyo ](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/family/free-playgrounds-in-tokyo/ \"The Best Free Playgrounds in Tokyo\")\nAugust 16, 2013 | Setsuko Yasuda \nTokyo is a treasure chest of free entertainment for families with small children and far more green and imaginative than you would expect from a concrete jungle. The good news is, most of them are either very free or very [[…]](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/family/free-playgrounds-in-tokyo/)\n[Family](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/family/)\n  * [ ![](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2013/05/nico-nico-park-entrance-1024x768.jpg) ](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/family/nico-nico-park-cheap-fun-with-the-kids/ \"Niko Niko Park – Cheap Fun with the Kids\")\n###  [ Niko Niko Park – Cheap Fun with the Kids ](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/family/nico-nico-park-cheap-fun-with-the-kids/ \"Niko Niko Park – Cheap Fun with the Kids\")\nMay 22, 2013 | Greg Lane \nTokyo parks get crowded. On weekends (especially if you have more than one small child) your kids will run off and disappear like ninjas on a moonless night. Due to the crowds, there also tend to be queues of 6 [[…]](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/family/nico-nico-park-cheap-fun-with-the-kids/)\n[Family](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/family/)\n  * [ ![](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2013/03/IMG_8671-1024x678.jpg) ](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/family/two-parks-for-the-price-of-one-inokashira-park-zoo/ \"Two Parks for the Price of One: Inokashira Park Zoo\")\n###  [ Two Parks for the Price of One: Inokashira Park Zoo ](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/family/two-parks-for-the-price-of-one-inokashira-park-zoo/ \"Two Parks for the Price of One: Inokashira Park Zoo\")\nMarch 19, 2013 | Grace Buchele Mineta \nThe mascot of Inokashira Park Zoo is a squirrel, so to be completely honest, you shouldn’t really be expecting much in terms of animal variety. However, at 400yen for a passport-less adult (with a passport, foreigners get a 20% discount), [[…]](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/family/two-parks-for-the-price-of-one-inokashira-park-zoo/)\n[Family](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/family/) [Themeparks and Zoos](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/themeparks-and-zoos/)\n\n\n  * [ ![](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/11/ubigi-logo-thumbnail.png) ](https://go.ubigi.com/eKO0kQ)\n###  [ Get a Ubigi eSIM for Japan (in advance!) ](https://go.ubigi.com/eKO0kQ \"Get a Ubigi eSIM for Japan \\(in advance!\\)\")\n[ Details ](https://go.ubigi.com/eKO0kQ)\n  * [ ![](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/01/IMG_6391-562x421.jpg) ~ ¥15,500 ](https://www.triptojapan.com/tours/join-sumo-wrestlers-for-a-match-and-lunch)\n###  [ Challenge Sumo Wrestlers and Enjoy Lunch ](https://www.triptojapan.com/tours/join-sumo-wrestlers-for-a-match-and-lunch \"Challenge Sumo Wrestlers and Enjoy Lunch\")\n[ Details ](https://www.triptojapan.com/tours/join-sumo-wrestlers-for-a-match-and-lunch)\n  * [ ![](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2019/09/early-morning-sumo-training-tokyo-4-mareike-dornhege-562x421.jpg) ~ ¥15,873 ](https://www.viator.com/tours/Tokyo/Tour-of-Sumo-Morning-Practice/d334-21490P10?pid=P00068523&mcid=42383&medium=link&medium_version=tour-ad)\n###  [ Sumo Morning Practice Tour at Stable in Tokyo ](https://www.viator.com/tours/Tokyo/Tour-of-Sumo-Morning-Practice/d334-21490P10?pid=P00068523&mcid=42383&medium=link&medium_version=tour-ad \"Sumo Morning Practice Tour at Stable in Tokyo\")\n[ Details ](https://www.viator.com/tours/Tokyo/Tour-of-Sumo-Morning-Practice/d334-21490P10?pid=P00068523&mcid=42383&medium=link&medium_version=tour-ad)\n  * [ ![transparent PNG](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/07/transparent.png) ](https://www.rekibun.or.jp/en/grutto/)\n###  [ Save on 100+ Museums, Gardens, and More Across Tokyo! ](https://www.rekibun.or.jp/en/grutto/ \"Save on 100+ Museums, Gardens, and More Across Tokyo!\")\n[ Details ](https://www.rekibun.or.jp/en/grutto/)\n  * [ ![The Hakone Ropeway over a plain of grasses and Mt Fuji in the background](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2017/06/GettyImages-934890264-562x421.jpg) ](https://www.triptojapan.com/trips/10-day-golden-route)\n###  [ See the Best of Japan with Trip To Japan ](https://www.triptojapan.com/trips/10-day-golden-route \"See the Best of Japan with Trip To Japan\")\n[ Details ](https://www.triptojapan.com/trips/10-day-golden-route)\n  * [ ![](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2017/03/kintsugi-experience_BigCircle-GettyImages-1330540475-562x421.jpg) ~ ¥9,000 ](https://www.triptojapan.com/tours/discover-the-art-of-kintsugi-in-the-heart-of-tokyo/)\n###  [ Experience the Traditional Art of Kintsugi ](https://www.triptojapan.com/tours/discover-the-art-of-kintsugi-in-the-heart-of-tokyo/ \"Experience the Traditional Art of Kintsugi\")\n[ Details ](https://www.triptojapan.com/tours/discover-the-art-of-kintsugi-in-the-heart-of-tokyo/)\n\n\n[ ![Scroll Up](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/themes/cheapo_theme/assets/icons/arrow-up-solid.svg.gzip) ](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/family/)\n##### About Tokyo Cheapo\n## About\nWith 500,000 - 800,000 readers each month, Tokyo Cheapo is the site of choice for value hunters who want their yen to go further in Tokyo. We cover all the basics including [things to do in Tokyo](https://tokyocheapo.com/living/101-free-and-cheap-things-to-do-in-tokyo/), how to [get from Narita airport to Tokyo](https://tokyocheapo.com/travel/transport/cheapest-transport-to-and-from-narita-airport/), [which JR rail pass to choose](https://tokyocheapo.com/travel/transport/which-jr-rail-pass-to-choose/), getting a [SIM card](https://tokyocheapo.com/business/internet/prepaid-cheap-japan-sim-card-options/) and [pocket wifi](https://tokyocheapo.com/business/internet/rent-wifi-router-japan/). \nTo find why we started this site, check out the [Tokyo Cheapo Manifesto](https://tokyocheapo.com/living/tokyo-cheapo-manifesto/ \"The Tokyo Cheapo Manifesto\"). For more about the people behind this site, check out the [profiles of the cheapos](https://tokyocheapo.com/cheapos/ \"The Cheapos\"). If you want to contribute, see [our careers page](https://fasttrainltd.com/careers/). For advertising and sponsorship of our Tokyo Cheapo channels, [get in touch here](https://fasttrainltd.com/#contact). \n**Affiliate Links**\nSome of the articles on this site contain affiliate links. If you purchase from or sign up with some companies we link to, we will be compensated. We don't endorse any of the companies we link to but we are selective in terms of the companies that we choose. You should exercise careful judgement with any online purchase. Additionally, the terms of all offers are subject to change without notice. \n**Sponsored Content**\nSponsored posts are clearly labeled with a \"Sponsored\" tag. Additionally, content such as tours and tickets, hotels and apartments are commercial content. \nFor more on the Tokyo Cheapo story, go to our [About Page](https://tokyocheapo.com/about/). \n![endless discovery logo](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/07/endless-discovery-logo-white.png)\n##### Site Map\n  * Locations\n  * [Akasaka](https://tokyocheapo.com/locations/central-tokyo/akasaka/)\n  * [Akihabara](https://tokyocheapo.com/locations/central-tokyo/akihabara-central-tokyo/)\n  * [Asakusa](https://tokyocheapo.com/locations/east-tokyo/asakusa/)\n  * [Ginza](https://tokyocheapo.com/locations/central-tokyo/ginza/)\n  * [Harajuku](https://tokyocheapo.com/locations/central-tokyo/harajuku/)\n  * [Odaiba](https://tokyocheapo.com/locations/central-tokyo/odaiba/)\n  * [Omotesandō](https://tokyocheapo.com/locations/central-tokyo/omotesando/)\n  * [Roppongi](https://tokyocheapo.com/locations/central-tokyo/roppongi/)\n  * [Shibuya](https://tokyocheapo.com/locations/central-tokyo/shibuya-2/)\n  * [Shimokitazawa](https://tokyocheapo.com/locations/west-tokyo/shimokitazawa-2/)\n  * [Shinjuku](https://tokyocheapo.com/locations/central-tokyo/shinjuku/)\n  * [Ueno](https://tokyocheapo.com/locations/east-tokyo/ueno/)\n  * [More](https://tokyocheapo.com/all-locations)\n\n\n  * Categories\n  * [Anime And Gaming](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/anime-and-gaming/)\n  * [Art](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/art/)\n  * [Business](https://tokyocheapo.com/business/)\n  * [Cafés](https://tokyocheapo.com/food-and-drink/cafe/)\n  * [Drinking](https://tokyocheapo.com/food-and-drink/drinking/)\n  *     * [Eating & Drinking](https://tokyocheapo.com/food-and-drink/)\n    * [Education](https://tokyocheapo.com/living/education/)\n    * [Events](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/event-posts/)\n    * [Family](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/family/)\n    * [Fashion](https://tokyocheapo.com/shopping-2/fashion/)\n    * [Financial](https://tokyocheapo.com/business/financial/)\n    * [Getting around](https://tokyocheapo.com/travel/)\n    * [Holidays](https://tokyocheapo.com/travel/holidays/)\n    * [Household](https://tokyocheapo.com/living/household/)\n    * [International Food](https://tokyocheapo.com/food-and-drink/international-food/)\n    * [Internet](https://tokyocheapo.com/business/internet/)\n    * [Japanese Culture And Tradition](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/japanese-culture-and-tradition/)\n    * [Lifestyle](https://tokyocheapo.com/lifestyle/)\n    * [Living](https://tokyocheapo.com/living/)\n    * [Movies, Shows and Theatre](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/movies-theatre/)\n    * [Museums And Exhibitions](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/museums-and-exhibitions/)\n    * [Music and Nightlife](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/music-and-nightlife/)\n    * [Outdoors and Nature](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/outdoors/)\n    * [Places to stay](https://tokyocheapo.com/accommodationcat/)\n    * [Podcast](https://tokyocheapo.com/podcast/)\n    * [Ramen](https://tokyocheapo.com/food-and-drink/ramen/)\n    * [Seasonal Activities](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/seasonal-activities/)\n    * [Shopping](https://tokyocheapo.com/shopping-2/)\n    * [Sightseeing](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/sightseeing/)\n    * [Snow Sports](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/snow-sports/)\